{
  "openapi": "3.0.1",
  "info": {
    "title": "默认模块",
    "description": "",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "认证"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/api/auth/user/send-register-code": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "发送终端用户注册邮箱验证码",
        "deprecated": false,
        "description": "用于终端用户（C端用户）注册，发送6位数字邮箱验证码到用户邮箱。\n\n**验证码类型**：邮箱验证码（6位数字）\n- 通过邮件发送到用户邮箱\n- 有效期：10分钟\n- 防刷机制：1分钟内不能重复发送\n- 用于：终端用户注册验证\n",
        "tags": [
          "认证"
        ],
        "parameters": [],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "email"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "email": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "format": "email",
                    "description": "邮箱地址（验证码将发送到此邮箱）",
                    "example": "user@example.com"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "邮箱验证码发送成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Success"
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "message": "Verification code sent to email",
                  "data": {
                    "expiresIn": 600
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {}
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "请求参数错误或邮箱已注册",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {}
          }
        },
        "security": []
      }
    },
    "/api/auth/user/register": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "终端用户注册（邮箱验证码注册 + 设备指纹）",
        "deprecated": false,
        "description": "注册时创建 User 账号，自动分配基础角色 basic_user（未认证用户）。后续可通过认证流程升级角色。\n\n**验证码类型**：邮箱验证码（6位数字）\n- 从用户邮箱中获取（通过 /api/auth/user/send-register-code 发送）\n- 格式：6位纯数字（如：123456）\n- 有效期：10分钟\n- 使用后自动失效\n\n**设备指纹**：可选参数，桌面端程序可以获取设备指纹并传入\n- 用于设备管理和数量限制控制\n- 如果提供，注册时会自动创建设备记录\n- 如果不提供，注册成功但不会创建设备记录（后续登录时也可以不提供设备指纹）\n",
        "tags": [
          "认证"
        ],
        "parameters": [],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "email",
                  "password",
                  "verificationCode"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "email": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "format": "email",
                    "description": "邮箱地址",
                    "example": "user@example.com"
                  },
                  "password": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "minLength": 6,
                    "maxLength": 50,
                    "description": "密码（6-50个字符）",
                    "example": "password123"
                  },
                  "verificationCode": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "pattern": "^\\d{6}$",
                    "description": "6位数字邮箱验证码（从邮箱中获取，通过 /api/auth/user/send-register-code 发送）",
                    "example": "123456"
                  },
                  "deviceFingerprint": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "minLength": 1,
                    "maxLength": 255,
                    "description": "设备指纹（可选，桌面端程序生成，用于设备管理和数量限制。如果提供，注册时会自动创建设备记录）",
                    "example": "device_fingerprint_hash_12345"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "注册成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Success"
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "message": "User registration successful",
                  "data": {
                    "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
                    "user": {
                      "id": "clx123456789",
                      "email": "user@example.com",
                      "role": "basic_user",
                      "status": "normal"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {}
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "请求参数错误、验证码错误或设备数量超限",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {}
          }
        },
        "security": []
      }
    },
    "/api/auth/user/login": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "终端用户登录（使用邮箱 + 密码 + 设备指纹）",
        "deprecated": false,
        "description": "终端用户（C端用户）登录接口，需要邮箱、密码和设备指纹。\n\n**注意**：终端用户登录不需要图形验证码，使用设备指纹进行安全验证。\n\n**设备指纹**：可选参数，桌面端程序可以获取设备指纹并传入\n- 用于设备管理和数量限制控制\n- 如果提供设备指纹：\n  - 如果设备已存在，会更新最后使用时间\n  - 如果设备不存在，会检查用户套餐的设备数量限制\n  - 超过设备数量限制时会返回错误\n- 如果不提供设备指纹，登录成功但不会创建设备记录\n",
        "tags": [
          "认证"
        ],
        "parameters": [],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "email",
                  "password"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "email": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "format": "email",
                    "description": "用户邮箱地址",
                    "example": "user@example.com"
                  },
                  "password": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "minLength": 6,
                    "description": "用户密码",
                    "example": "password123"
                  },
                  "deviceFingerprint": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "minLength": 1,
                    "maxLength": 255,
                    "description": "设备指纹（可选，桌面端程序生成，用于设备管理和数量限制。如果提供，登录时会自动创建设备记录）",
                    "example": "device_fingerprint_hash_12345"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "登录成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Success"
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "message": "Login successful",
                  "data": {
                    "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
                    "user": {
                      "id": "clx123456789",
                      "email": "user@example.com",
                      "phone": null,
                      "role": "basic_user",
                      "status": "normal"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {}
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "请求参数错误或设备数量超限",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {}
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "登录失败（邮箱/密码错误或账号状态异常）",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {}
          }
        },
        "security": []
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "schemas": {
      "Error": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "success": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "example": false
          },
          "message": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "Error message"
          },
          "errors": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {}
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "Success": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "success": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "example": true
          },
          "message": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "Success message"
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {}
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "responses": {},
    "securitySchemes": {}
  },
  "servers": [],
  "security": []
}